      "text": "Autumn leaves",
      "translation": "秋叶"
    },
    {
      "time": 44.99,
      "time_str": "00:44.990",
      "text": "The falling leaves drift by the window",
      "translation": "落叶飘过窗前"
    },
    {
      "time": 55.369,
      "time_str": "00:55.369",
      "text": "The autumn leaves of red and gold",
      "translation": "那红金色的秋叶"
    },
    {
      "time": 67.99,
      "time_str": "01:07.990",
      "text": "I see your lips, the summer kisses",
      "translation": "仿佛你夏日的吻"
    },
    {
      "time": 77.73,
      "time_str": "01:17.730",
      "text": "The sunburned hand I used to hold",
      "translation": "和我曾牵的晒伤的手"
    },
    {
      "time": 89.9,
      "time_str": "01:29.900",
      "text": "Since you went away the days grow long",
      "translation": "自你离去后白昼漫长"
    },
    {
      "time": 100.37,
      "time_str": "01:40.370",
      "text": "And soon I‘‘ll hear old winter‘‘s song",
      "translation": "很快将听见冬日的歌"
    },
    {
      "time": 112.139,
      "time_str": "01:52.139",
      "text": "But I miss you most of all, my darling",
      "translation": "但我最思念你 亲爱的"
    },
    {
